Placeholder. Vite copies everything in frontend/public/ into frontend/dist/ on
every build, which is the only reason frontend/dist/gitkeep survives.

main.go embeds frontend/dist with //go:embed, and that fails to compile if the
directory is empty. Vite empties dist/ on each build, so without this file the
placeholder would disappear the first time anyone ran a build and every
subsequent `go build` on a clean tree would fail. See .gitignore.
